sequenceDiagram
    participant A as "Front / App"
    participant W as "WAS"
    participant F as "FastAPI /chat"
    participant P as "preprocess"
    participant I as "intent"
    participant G as "generate / persona"

    A->>W: "캐주얼 또는 모호한 메시지"
    W->>F: "POST /chat"
    F->>P: "활성 세션 state 로드"
    P-->>F: "추가 WAS refresh 없음"
    F->>I: "intent 분석"
    I-->>F: "casual 또는 fallback"
    F->>G: "간단 응답 생성"
    G-->>F: "response"
    F-->>W: "ChatResponse"
    W-->>A: "최종 응답"
    Note over F: "활성 세션이면 추가 FastAPI -> WAS read/write 없음"
